author: lgo
msg: Fix dirent_uri tests on Windows when the tests are run from another drive as
C:, as is the case for the Windows buildbot.
* subversion/tests/libsvn_subr/dirent_uri-test.c
(global): Define getdcwd as alias for _getdcwd.
(test_dirent_get_absolute): Use getdcwd to get the current directory of the
C: drive to build the expected paths to match with the testcases which all
use C: (as that's the only drive letter we're sure to exist).
